{"tid":1747234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［我諗我下世要做樹］ 用左1蚊雞找卡數果啲入一入黎","createTime":"2019-11-23T06:34:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T07:42:00.000Z","uid":1082,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3072b807a9c1f26d969242ebfecc92a831af6449","tid":1747234,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:34:35.000Z","msg":"話說小弟上個月pps 找左 千四蚊卡數<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後就順手cut 埋張credit card. 今日就收到11 封呢啲咁既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3pPMsWy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3pPMsWy.jpg&h=a1083f48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我起初以為係啲咩特別野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能我cut卡永隆send 個summary 比我，或者周到我之前用1 蚊找卡數，告鳩我之類咁既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知一打開，封封都係3頁紙月結單，加埋份私隱聲明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hXJdSsv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhXJdSsv.jpg&h=72d821bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n月結單total 31頁，所以有11封<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3a39qLa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3a39qLa.jpg&h=5c90f991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開晒啲信之後，望住疊紙同埋果千幾行1蚊雞record，我果刻真係好有成就感<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/43kf5LS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F43kf5LS.jpg&h=d10327a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RAJtGj4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRAJtGj4.jpg&h=d3c3c742&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有冇其他人都收到咁大疊紙，分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f73c173f12eeaa1a8679a9bac69ac5aaefd433d0","tid":1747234,"uid":1082,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:35:43.000Z","msg":"我老母啱啱仲問我發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ceac350512536011a46320a46d83706733b853","tid":1747234,"uid":162674,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:36:45.000Z","msg":"環保團體表示這樣我們完全不能接受的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859b8df99ef6719a110a3648384c93deb38257fb","tid":1747234,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:36:55.000Z","msg":"永隆得罪你？"},{"pid":"a035c0788d91aba1ab9cd33bacdfef2a5e5d5692","tid":1747234,"uid":85118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"59ceac350512536011a46320a46d83706733b853","tid":1747234,"uid":162674,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:36:45.000Z","msg":"環保團體表示這樣我們完全不能接受的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:38:21